===Etymology===
{{etyl|ang}} {{term|þreat|þrēat|crowd, army}}.

===Pronunciation===
* {{a|UK}} {{IPA|/θrɛt/}}
* {{enPR|thrĕt}}, {{SAMPA|/TrEt/}}
* {{audio|en-us-threat.ogg|Audio (US)}}

